Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.23,0:00:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.43,0:00:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那一天的梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.13,0:00:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,未能和你一起过完的那个季节…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.03,0:00:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祈祷着能够永远继续下去…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.80,0:00:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那闪耀着的午后阳光…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.54,0:00:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反复做着相同的梦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.61,0:00:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像坏掉的唱片一样…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.77,0:00:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知已经重复了多少次…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.64,0:00:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有时间的黄昏的天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.65,0:01:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进行着一段永远的旅程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.66,0:01:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冰冷的指尖继续探索着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.04,0:01:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,碎片发出光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.11,0:01:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紧紧的抱住胸口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.55,0:01:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寻找遗失的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.66,0:01:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用双手的掌心确认
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.03,0:01:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相遇在新的早晨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.40,0:01:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时间开始流动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.65,0:02:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,川澄同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.09,0:02:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有事情找你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.65,0:02:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以跟我们来一下吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.09,0:02:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「狐狸与葡萄」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.73,0:02:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有证据能证明\N玻璃是她打破的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.40,0:02:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.20,0:02:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.77,0:02:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过 也没有证据能证明不是她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.10,0:02:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？这是怎么一回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.94,0:02:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经是第三次了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.77,0:02:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自从小舞的问题发生以来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.94,0:02:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐佑理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.28,0:02:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没做的话说清楚不就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.19,0:02:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过因为小舞的性格使然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.29,0:02:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以她什么都没说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.39,0:02:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她怎么可能说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.09,0:02:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打破玻璃的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.63,0:02:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是盘据在学校里看不见的怪物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.06,0:02:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种事情说出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.36,0:02:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不可能有人会相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.90,0:03:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以学生会盯上了小舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.47,0:03:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,常常找她麻烦\N总是特别被叫出来解释
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.47,0:03:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小舞总是一直没有反应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.01,0:03:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是一直被指责
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.75,0:03:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后默默地接受处罚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.81,0:03:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,处罚？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.32,0:03:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上次还被停学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.32,0:03:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.06,0:03:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该不会是跟你谈有关停学的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.92,0:03:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是 只是挨骂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.70,0:03:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经开始上课了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.46,0:03:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赶快回教室去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.77,0:03:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是 我们走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.07,0:03:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仓田同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.24,0:03:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最好不要跟那种家伙\N走的那么近比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.38,0:03:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信小舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.39,0:03:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真气人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.73,0:03:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真凶啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.13,0:03:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能不凶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.53,0:04:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久濑那家伙说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.20,0:04:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最好不要跟那种家伙走的那么近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.23,0:04:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他把人看成什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.47,0:04:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也要劝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.11,0:04:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要太接近川澄舞比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.94,0:04:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过事情不是这样子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.41,0:04:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心情不好的时候\N就是肚子饿的证据喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.72,0:04:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,商店街有一间咖哩专卖店\N咖哩很好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.35,0:04:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要一起去吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.22,0:04:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咖哩？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.99,0:04:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店长是印度人喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.16,0:04:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…这是没关系啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.63,0:04:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的社团活动呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.46,0:04:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天休息喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.53,0:04:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.80,0:04:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你先去校门口等我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.90,0:04:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我等你喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.44,0:04:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感情真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.61,0:04:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是一起吃顿饭\N不要这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.28,0:04:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.52,0:04:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,栞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.49,0:05:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个…昨天真是谢谢你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.03,0:05:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要说谢谢就去跟小舞说吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.40,0:05:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小舞？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.70,0:05:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把狗赶走的那个人吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.17,0:05:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不过她是相当奇怪的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.67,0:05:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个人真酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.88,0:05:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像王子一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.78,0:05:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王子？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.45,0:05:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在女孩有危险时\N前来搭救的王子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.02,0:05:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能想象那种真正的恋爱\N开始的情境吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.42,0:05:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请不要嘲笑我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.72,0:05:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近没有这样的连续剧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.06,0:05:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再怎么说…小舞是女孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.73,0:05:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.36,0:05:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过…真令人向往
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.33,0:05:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那种像连续剧一般的相遇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.50,0:05:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了 你还没吃午饭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.60,0:05:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要一起去吃咖哩饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.67,0:05:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怕吃辣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.28,0:05:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真像小孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.31,0:05:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像这样子说别人很讨厌耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.15,0:05:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 要吃什么呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.25,0:06:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冰淇淋如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.86,0:06:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冰淇淋…那种冷冷的冰吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.69,0:06:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有热的冰吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.24,0:06:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.54,0:06:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你等我一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.71,0:06:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.64,0:06:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜欢香草冰淇淋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.81,0:06:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一要吃吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.91,0:06:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.42,0:06:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.72,0:06:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.85,0:06:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不敢相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.39,0:06:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在冬天不能吃冰淇淋吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.86,0:06:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是 我不是在说这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.56,0:06:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再怎么看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.20,0:06:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也看不出因为感冒而休学的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.33,0:06:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了 佑一你不吃午饭吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.07,0:06:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 名雪还在校门等我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.04,0:06:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.94,0:07:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完了完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.89,0:07:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.89,0:07:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,骗子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.46,0:07:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.46,0:07:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等了很久你都没有来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.70,0:07:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以为你已经先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.54,0:07:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在咖哩专卖店也没看到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.14,0:07:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以为你先回家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.84,0:07:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以决定买肉包回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.64,0:07:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是没看到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.31,0:07:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我都说对不起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.35,0:07:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了表示歉意\N你说什么我都答应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.78,0:07:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.28,0:07:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那明天是星期日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.49,0:07:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以陪我去买东西吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.09,0:07:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也要去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.06,0:07:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说什么“我也要去”的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.09,0:07:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你已经不恨我了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.86,0:07:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了 白天休战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.00,0:07:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.54,0:08:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随便你 把我的漫画还来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.94,0:08:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想看就自己去买嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.48,0:08:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你自己也有钱对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.68,0:08:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也能买漫画吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.25,0:08:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,买不买是由你决定的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.08,0:08:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个也能买吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.68,0:08:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.22,0:08:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以喔 去商店街的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.96,0:08:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.10,0:08:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 佑一你太过分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.34,0:08:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有叫我就自己把晚餐吃完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.38,0:08:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.84,0:08:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都已经什么时候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.95,0:08:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经叫你好几次了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.38,0:08:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“饭已经做好啰 ”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.12,0:08:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没听到啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.69,0:08:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你因为看漫画太入神\N所以才没听到吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.22,0:08:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要吃就自己去冰箱\N找些东西煮来吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.69,0:08:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不要再麻烦秋子阿姨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.93,0:09:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一大笨蛋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.93,0:09:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然在这里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.36,0:09:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天才有过骚动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.90,0:09:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是被值班老师发现\N可就不妙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.44,0:09:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎样了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.64,0:09:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我也算是共犯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.14,0:09:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要吃吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.51,0:09:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.75,0:09:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些鬼怪是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.25,0:09:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不只一只吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.62,0:09:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要战斗呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.49,0:10:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是有谁拜托你吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.49,0:10:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要一直不说话\N你就说些什么嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.86,0:10:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近 鬼怪开始骚动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.43,0:10:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在鬼怪还没完全消灭以前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.77,0:10:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是不会离开的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.24,0:10:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么意思…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.57,0:10:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么东西？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.91,0:10:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鬼怪来了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.12,0:10:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 现在不是吃东西的时候吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.52,0:10:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.59,0:10:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.22,0:10:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪出来啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.73,0:10:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…你做什么啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.23,0:10:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是我要问的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.23,0:10:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你跑来这做什么啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.23,0:10:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要做什么是我的事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.07,0:10:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肿出包包来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.81,0:10:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乖 乖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.64,0:10:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把我当三岁小孩吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.21,0:10:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想你想要我这样做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.15,0:10:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是谁\N真是危险的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.08,0:11:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在说别人之前先说说你自己吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.19,0:11:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 有谁在里面吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.99,0:11:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好了 快逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.32,0:11:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 在那里做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.26,0:11:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.57,0:11:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是恐怖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.38,0:11:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这都是谁的错啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.88,0:11:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小舞 总之今天先回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.98,0:11:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鬼怪一定也有不出现的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.92,0:11:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.42,0:11:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鳕鱼子饭团…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.12,0:11:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在挂念那个啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.72,0:11:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有蟹肉美乃滋饭团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.99,0:11:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那种东西再买就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.50,0:11:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.73,0:11:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.57,0:11:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 一定要回去喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.90,0:11:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.47,0:11:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也要去买饭团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.31,0:11:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己拿钱去买
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.08,0:12:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你身上有带吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.29,0:12:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我出门了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.79,0:12:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.07,0:12:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小猫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.28,0:12:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是小猫也没什么稀奇的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.35,0:12:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过好可爱喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.41,0:12:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小猫咪 小猫咪…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.35,0:12:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.62,0:12:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.55,0:12:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要碰它呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.52,0:12:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好想摸一摸它 抱一抱它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.36,0:12:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要靠近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.43,0:12:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不然猫过敏又会发作喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.97,0:13:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是碰了猫以后\N眼泪就会流个不停吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.54,0:13:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想起来了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.34,0:13:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说是不是想起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.27,0:13:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想是想起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.11,0:13:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.51,0:13:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这只小猫 可以养在家里吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.48,0:13:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名雪 我会找到\N能养这只猫的饲主的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.05,0:13:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要 我要养这只猫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.52,0:13:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好喜欢小猫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.70,0:13:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一 还记得吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.36,0:13:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候你对我说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.00,0:13:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会做出\N能医好对猫过敏的药哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.67,0:13:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.64,0:13:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.78,0:13:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可是没有当医生的脑袋喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.08,0:13:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要有斗志喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.52,0:13:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,世上还是有就算努力\N也做不到的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.79,0:13:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以后说不定还会想起更多\N有关以前的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.56,0:13:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.03,0:14:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名雪说得对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.13,0:14:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说不定会一点一点的想起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.50,0:14:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小时候在这里经历过的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.64,0:14:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是 真琴？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.71,0:14:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 真琴你在那做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.95,0:14:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么丢下我\N自己一个人跑掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.95,0:14:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是谁睡的跟猪一样啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.56,0:14:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帮忙买东西吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.56,0:14:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有买齐吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.73,0:14:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经买齐了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.03,0:14:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经是大人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.76,0:14:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.13,0:14:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 这样啊 那么顺便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.37,0:14:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想要买的东西也能拜托你吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.84,0:14:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 我帮你去买
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.88,0:14:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.75,0:14:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 包在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.42,0:14:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道放在哪里的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.12,0:14:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以问问店员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.82,0:14:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请他随便推荐一本就行了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.82,0:14:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.73,0:15:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你拜托她买什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.23,0:15:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看着就对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.03,0:15:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请问…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.90,0:15:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.30,0:15:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黄色书刊放在哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.84,0:15:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请给我黄色书刊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.27,0:15:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请推荐我几本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.01,0:15:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个笨蛋 这么大声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.08,0:15:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴 赶快走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.42,0:15:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的脸是不是红到烧起来了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.29,0:15:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你会真的跑去买了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.06,0:15:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么一回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.73,0:15:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一要买的东西是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.93,0:15:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是低级
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.23,0:15:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为 你都说你已经是大人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.00,0:15:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.74,0:15:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子哪会买那种书啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.14,0:15:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混…混蛋\N真琴…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.98,0:15:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是佑一不对喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.52,0:16:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想这种风雪夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.82,0:16:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她应该不会跑去消灭鬼怪吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.63,0:16:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,浴室没人喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.20,0:16:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙平常要是也像这样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.73,0:16:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是满可爱的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.74,0:16:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么味道？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.54,0:16:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有放温泉精之类的东西进去吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.44,0:16:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过 仔细一闻\N这个味道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.45,0:16:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.48,0:16:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 怎么了\N发生什么事了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.95,0:16:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,浴缸里有味噌汤耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.39,0:16:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没人放的话\N怎么会有味噌汤在里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.73,0:16:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你明白吗\N好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.46,0:16:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个…难道说\N她把整包味噌都放进去了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.93,0:16:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个月可头痛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.10,0:16:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道要把这些全部喝掉吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.54,0:16:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.07,0:16:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴 浪费食物是不行的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.11,0:17:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.91,0:17:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她没有在反省
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.11,0:17:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看她那样子绝对没有在反省
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.36,0:17:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次又是什么事了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.03,0:17:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是烟火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.13,0:17:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 半夜还放什么烟火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.43,0:17:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙会打扰到邻居的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.00,0:17:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.83,0:17:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…那只手拿的东西是什么啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.54,0:17:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烟火 是你放的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.38,0:17:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烟火是在外面才能放的东西喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.71,0:17:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等到天气暖和点\N大家再一起放吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.45,0:17:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.35,0:17:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么…现在已经很晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.42,0:17:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家快去睡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.89,0:17:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.36,0:17:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.72,0:17:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.13,0:17:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.33,0:17:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.97,0:17:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安 佑一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.54,0:18:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安 起的真早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.84,0:18:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有 真琴…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.44,0:18:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安 佑一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.47,0:18:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦 你…你在做什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.58,0:18:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃早餐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.78,0:18:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看也知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.01,0:18:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿垃圾出去时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.68,0:18:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为偶然遇到亚由？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.85,0:18:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就问她要不要一起吃早餐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.25,0:18:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请不要在路边遇到\N就邀人家来吃饭嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.86,0:18:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.66,0:18:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的意见不重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.99,0:18:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也认为没关系喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.13,0:18:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.20,0:18:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候感情变这么好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.40,0:18:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你的招待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.84,0:18:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是粗茶淡饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.24,0:18:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我们出发吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.64,0:18:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.81,0:18:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说什么早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.48,0:18:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃 睡 看漫画\N你还真是好命啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.05,0:18:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一 你说得太过分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.39,0:18:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.03,0:19:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴 回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.07,0:19:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫你回去你有听到吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.94,0:19:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她太可怜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.74,0:19:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是不了解那家伙才会这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.11,0:19:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果发生什么事就是佑一的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.25,0:19:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你叫她一个人回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.58,0:19:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是她自己可能回不去喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.15,0:19:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.02,0:19:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.12,0:19:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我送她回去\N其它的事就拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.89,0:19:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.16,0:19:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿出你的魄力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.36,0:19:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你到底在想什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.93,0:19:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉 这下肯定迟到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.47,0:19:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我讨厌自己一个人在家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.97,0:19:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秋子阿姨也出去工作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.51,0:19:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,家里只有我一个人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.38,0:19:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么东西？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.81,0:19:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙 不就是昨天那只猫吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.51,0:19:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.62,0:19:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.22,0:19:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也是孤单一个吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.92,0:20:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管走到哪里都是孤单一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.76,0:20:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把这家伙带回家养如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.06,0:20:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要你说要养
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.16,0:20:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秋子阿姨很快就会答应的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.00,0:20:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然名雪会有点问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.90,0:20:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过只要不要太接近的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.47,0:20:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样它就太可怜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.14,0:20:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可怜？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.68,0:20:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算随随便便被人饲养会幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.01,0:20:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是被抛弃时是会很痛苦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.98,0:20:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怀念着温暖的棉被和好吃的饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.35,0:20:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这样悲伤着 直到死去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.52,0:20:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,野生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.26,0:20:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就该让它依照原本的方式生活\N放着不管也没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.03,0:20:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它可不是野生的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.96,0:20:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放着它不管反而危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.67,0:20:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你来照顾它不就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.47,0:20:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,动物有着只要不被需要\N就马上会被丢弃的命运
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.38,0:20:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 太靠近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.54,0:20:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.28,0:21:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.19,0:21:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是佑一你的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.59,0:21:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一没有跟我抢的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.83,0:21:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一你这笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.98,0:21:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.38,0:21:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.17,0:21:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秋子阿姨 真琴呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.47,0:21:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道…回来后马上又出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.04,0:21:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.88,0:22:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那时我直接就想到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.35,0:22:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙已经离开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.02,0:22:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过 会是去哪里…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.48,0:22:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个家伙有去处吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.37,0:22:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从随风飘流的云朵之间\N窥视到晴空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.28,0:22:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就连熟悉的街道也闪闪发光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.62,0:22:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向前奔跑的小小的背影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.00,0:23:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当时的两个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.27,0:23:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用天真来盖过溢出的疼痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.65,0:23:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时间静悄悄的流动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.49,0:23:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吹拂着温柔的风
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.23,0:23:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为冻僵的思念也会化做笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.34,0:23:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对封闭内心的真琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.11,0:23:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说着梦想的栞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.74,0:23:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,眼神黯淡的小舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.71,0:23:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我到底能为她们做些什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.18,0:23:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanon第6话\N她们的想法
